    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎光临地城</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/fb78a0c405ddc87814a64c53795ead40.poster.avif?t=1771541746\" width=854 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/fb78a0c405ddc87814a64c53795ead40.webm?t=1771541746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/fb78a0c405ddc87814a64c53795ead40.mp4?t=1771541746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >皇帝渴望黄金，而身为巫师的你必须想办法取得。带上两枚棋子：城堡和弓箭手，或许再配上一两种法术，深入深渊探险。升级你的队伍，习得新技能，并揭开黑暗深处的真相。你可以使用获得的黄金助你生存，或是冒着生命危险将黄金献给皇帝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>棋艺与乐趣的结合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/4623979c7bc7f23e4c150d6ca6393b2e.poster.avif?t=1771541746\" width=854 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/4623979c7bc7f23e4c150d6ca6393b2e.webm?t=1771541746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需记忆开局，没有冗长的残局，也不会陷入僵局。不同于传统的十六枚棋子，你只需从一枚棋子开始！随着棋局推进，可以召唤拥有独特能力的新棋子加入战场。别担心，也无需过度思考，敌人的移动方式很简单，除非——你遇上地城的头目……你可以收集“悔棋代币”以备不时之需，或者选择收集更多黄金！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你并不孤单</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/29952987aa2aa1b80fe1f8d93a4b2fda.avif?t=1771541746\" width=1560 height=397 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的史诗级胜利分享至社群并发起挑战吧！你可以观看其他高手玩家的胜利重播，并通过每日任务进一步打磨技巧。在自订棋盘编辑系统中，你还可以创建和下载全新的房间，为你的地城增添更多变化，在这场棋局中畅享更多乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>测验请回答</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883920/extras/27a03ac024a7479d24fd28569dfc0ae8.avif?t=1771541746\" width=1560 height=528 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在深入地城的过程中，会出现一些小测验，内容是根据你当下的心理状态与对棋子的想法提出的简单问题。你可以放心、真诚地作答，你的回答不会被用来设计针对你的策略。</p>",
